Honey Butter

- 2 sticks butter
Leave butter out to warm to room temperature. Or carefully use microwave to heat without any melting.

Cut up butter and put pieces in a cup just barely big enough to fit the end of an immersion blender. Blend until uniformly light and fluffy.

- 230g powdered sugar
Add sugar and and blend until mixed

- 2/3 cup honey
Add honey and blend until uniform, smooth and fluffy.

Unused portions can be frozen.

